Class InstanceIdentifierUtils

  • public class InstanceIdentifierUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains utility methods for converting an MD-SAL YangInstanceIdentifier to and from other representations.

    The representations convered for now are,

    • Protocol Buffer
